# A xterm-256color based TERMINFO that adds the escape sequences for italic.
#
# Note this overrides the default 'xterm-256color'.
#
# You could change this string below to something different, but 
# then you'd have to set it like 'TERM=<something different>'
#
# Install:
#
#   tic ./terminfo-italics
#
# References:
# - https://gist.github.com/sos4nt/3187620
# - https://github.com/joshdick/onedark.vim/issues/97
xterm-256color|xterm with 256 colors and italic,
    sitm=\E[3m, ritm=\E[23m,
    use=xterm-256color,
